<h2>About Metropolitan Cultural Council</h2>
<p class="lead">Celebrating Arts, Culture, and Community since our founding.</p>
<p>The Metropolitan Cultural Council is dedicated to promoting and supporting local cultural events across our community. We bring together concerts, theatre, exhibitions, workshops, and sports events to create unforgettable experiences for everyone.</p>
<p>Our mission is to make culture accessible, foster creativity, and strengthen community bonds through the power of the arts.</p>
